      p We're using technology to simplify the entire health insurance experience. You can use our app to talk to a doctor and get prescriptions without ever leaving home. Keep track of your health history with a timeline and earn rewards for staying active with a free Misfit step tracker.
      img(src="./images/ModernTechnology.png")

    form
      img(src="./images/OscarAlmost.png")
      h2 Oscar is for (almost) everyone
      p We currently offer plans to individuals, couples, and families living in parts of New York, New Jersey, California and Texas who don't already receive health insurance from an employer. If you're not in our area, stay tuned. We're expanding quickly.

